		<div id="comment_body_64666974"><p>About time. I have long been complaining to Amazon about selling products without UL safety certification or worse - fake UL safety certification. This is very simple to enforce, if it has an AC plug it has to have UL certification. UL is a safety inspection. They inspect the products for fire and shock hazards.</p></div>
	</div>

